entry.tran: (人、动物进食时)大声地咬，嚼得很响
entry.def: If a person or animal chomps their way through food or chomps on food, they chew it noisily.

example.ex: On the diet I would chomp my way through breakfast, even though I'm never hungry in the morning...
example.tran: 根据这一饮食计划，早餐时我需要大吃一顿，尽管我早上从来不饿。

example.ex: I chomped hungrily through the large steak...
example.tran: 我狼吞虎咽地吃着那一大块牛排。
